20170302 
clash over deities: Curfew in UP district after clashes over objectionable video clip on deities 
2-3-2017 
LUCKNOW: Curfew was imposed in Lakhimpur Kheri district on Thursday following communal clashes after an inflammatory video clip shot and uploaded by two local youths went viral. One of the youths was reportedly seen using foul language for Hindu deities in the clip. Two people suffered gunshot injuries in the clashes.All educational institutes in the district have been closed till further orders. With almost half the district police strength already out of station on election duty, additional police force was being rushed to the trouble-hit areas from adjoining districts. 
